{
  "date_key": "2026-03-25",
  "date_cn": "2026年03月25日",
  "day_cn": "周三",
  "english": "<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#1a73e8\">人际关系与友谊 Friendship, Trust &amp; Communication</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A (Megan): Hey, so… I need to vent for a sec. You know how I&#x27;ve been <strong>ride or die</strong> with Chloe since, like, middle school?</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B (Jake): Oh yeah, you two have always been super tight. What happened?</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Okay so last week she totally <strong>left me on read</strong> for three days after I asked if she was okay. Then she goes and posts stories hanging out with her new work friends like nothing&#x27;s wrong.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Hmm. I mean, that stings, but maybe she just needed space? Sometimes people aren&#x27;t trying to be shady — they&#x27;re just <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">dealing with their own stuff</span>.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I get that, but here&#x27;s the thing — when I finally called her out on it, she tried to <strong>gaslight</strong> me. She was like, &quot;I never saw your message,&quot; even though I could literally see the read receipts.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yikes. That&#x27;s not cool. But real talk — did you <strong>come at her</strong> super aggressive, or did you keep it chill?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Honestly? I probably came in a little hot. But I was hurt! I feel like I always <strong>have her back</strong>, and she just <strong>blows me off</strong> whenever something better comes along.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I hear you. Look, I don&#x27;t wanna <strong>stir the pot</strong>, but have you considered that maybe you guys are just in different chapters right now? It doesn&#x27;t mean the friendship is over. Sometimes people <strong>grow apart</strong> and that&#x27;s just life.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah… my sister said the same thing. She told me to stop <strong>reading into</strong> every little thing and just give Chloe some grace.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Your sister&#x27;s <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">spot on</span>. And hey — if Chloe&#x27;s really your girl, she&#x27;ll come around. But you gotta <strong>keep it real</strong> with her too. Just sit down, no drama, and tell her how you actually feel. Like, <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">lay your cards on the table</span>.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">You&#x27;re right. I think I&#x27;ve been so <strong>in my head</strong> about it that I made it worse than it needs to be. I&#x27;ll text her tonight and ask if she wants to grab coffee this weekend.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">There you go. Worst case, you get closure. Best case, you guys <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">hash it out</span> and come back even stronger.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Thanks, Jake. Seriously. You always know how to talk me off the ledge.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That&#x27;s what friends are for, Meg.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A（Megan）：嘿，我得吐槽一下。你知道我从初中开始就跟 Chloe 是<strong>生死之交</strong>（ride or die）吧？</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B（Jake）：当然啦，你俩一直关系特别铁。怎么了？</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：上周我发消息问她还好吗，她直接<strong>已读不回</strong>（left me on read）了三天。然后转头就发动态跟她新同事们玩得开开心心，好像什么事都没有。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：嗯……确实挺扎心的，但也许她只是需要一点空间？有时候人家不是故意搞事，只是在<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">处理自己的事情</span>。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：我理解，但问题是——我后来质问她的时候，她居然想<strong>PUA我 / 操控我认知</strong>（gaslight）。她说&quot;我没看到你的消息&quot;，但我明明能看到已读回执啊。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：呃……那确实不太行。但说真的——你<strong>质问她</strong>（come at her）的时候，语气是不是太冲了？</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：说实话？可能有点上头。但我真的很受伤啊！我觉得我一直<strong>挺她</strong>（have her back），而她一有更好的选择就<strong>甩开我</strong>（blow me off）。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：我懂。我不想<strong>搅局 / 挑事</strong>（stir the pot），但你有没有想过，也许你们只是处在人生不同的阶段？这不代表友谊就结束了。有时候人就是会<strong>渐行渐远</strong>（grow apart），这就是生活。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：嗯……我姐也这么说的。她让我别什么事都<strong>过度解读</strong>（read into），对 Chloe 宽容一点。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：你姐说得<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">太对了</span>。而且——如果 Chloe 真的是你的好朋友，她会回来的。但你也得<strong>坦诚相待</strong>（keep it real）。坐下来，别搞得太戏剧化，跟她说你真实的感受，<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">把话摊开说</span>。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：你说得对。我觉得我一直<strong>钻牛角尖</strong>（in my head），把事情想得比实际更严重了。我今晚给她发消息，问她周末要不要出来喝杯咖啡。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：这就对了。最坏的结果，你得到一个了结。最好的结果，你们<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">把问题聊开</span>，关系反而更好。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">A：谢谢你，Jake。真的。你总能让我冷静下来。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">B：这就是朋友的意义啊，Meg。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>ride or die</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 生死之交；最铁的朋友，无论什么情况都力挺对方</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用（源自嘻哈文化，现已广泛使用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容最亲密的朋友或伴侣关系</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>left me on read</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 已读不回</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / Gen Z</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 聊社交媒体和短信沟通时常用，表达被忽略的失落感</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>gaslight</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 操控他人认知，让对方怀疑自己的判断或记忆（心理操控）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全球通用英语（美国尤其高频使用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 讨论人际关系中的不健康行为、情感操控</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">04.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>come at someone</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 冲着某人来；以攻击性/对抗性的态度对待某人</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 描述争吵或质问时语气过于强硬</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">05.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>have someone&#x27;s back</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 挺某人，支持某人，在背后保护某人</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 表达对朋友的忠诚和支持</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">06.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>blow someone off</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 放某人鸽子；无视某人；不把某人当回事</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 抱怨朋友取消计划或忽略自己</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">07.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>stir the pot</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 搅局；挑事；故意把事情搞复杂</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 在给别人建议时，表明自己不想制造更多矛盾</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">08.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>grow apart</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— （两人之间）渐渐疏远，渐行渐远</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全球通用英语</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 描述友谊或感情随时间自然变淡</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">09.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>read into something</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 过度解读某事；想太多</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 劝人不要把简单的事情想得太复杂</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">10.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>keep it real</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 坦诚相待；说真话；做真实的自己</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用（源自非裔美国人口语，已广泛使用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 鼓励朋友在沟通中保持真诚</span></td></tr></table>",
  "beauty": "<div style=\"background:#fce4ec;border-left:4px solid #e91e8c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#c2185b;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#c2185b\">修容高光 · 圆脸&quot;瘦&quot;三圈的光影魔法</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">一、修容篇——把&quot;圆&quot;变成&quot;鹅蛋&quot;</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 1 选对修容色调</div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">棱橄榄皮最常踩的坑：用灰调修容 → 脸上脏兮兮。</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">✅ 正确思路：选 <strong>偏暖棕/焦糖棕</strong> 色调的修容，与你自身的黄暖肤色融为一体，阴影才像&quot;天生长在脸上&quot;。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 2 圆脸五区修容法（重点区域 + 手法）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 区域 | 目的 | 手法要点 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|------|----------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| ① <strong>太阳穴→颧骨下方</strong> | 收窄中庭宽度（最关键！） | 用修容刷从耳前向嘴角方向斜扫&quot;3&quot;字形，<strong>不超过瞳孔正下方</strong>，否则显脸更短 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| ② <strong>下颌角→下巴两侧</strong> | 削弱圆润轮廓线 | 顺着下颌骨向下巴方向轻扫，收窄下半张脸 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| ③ <strong>发际线两侧（额角）</strong> | 缩小额头横向宽度 | 沿发际线半圆形轻扫，面积不宜过大 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| ④ <strong>鼻梁两侧</strong> | 集中五官、视觉拉长中庭 | 眉头下方→鼻翼两侧细线条，用小号刷晕开 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| ⑤ <strong>下巴底部（颏下三角）</strong> | 制造下巴&quot;尖&quot;的错觉 | 下巴最下缘轻轻带过，让下巴在视觉上往前&quot;翘&quot;出来 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 3 晕染铁律</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>工具</strong>：用 <strong>松散的扇形刷 / 蘑菇头刷</strong> 打圈晕染，绝对不要硬边。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>手法</strong>：少量多次！先在手背试色，每次蘸取后在手背蹭掉多余粉量再上脸。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>顺序</strong>：先修容 → 再高光 → 最后腮红，三步叠加才不会互相盖掉。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">二、高光篇——橄榄皮的&quot;高级光泽&quot;</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 1 高光质地选择</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 质地 | 适合场景 | 棱橄榄皮适配度 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|----------|----------------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>细腻缎光 / 香槟光</strong> | 日常通勤 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 首选！ |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 水光 / 液体高光 | 拍照、派对 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ 混合底妆用，少量即可 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 大亮片闪光 | 舞台 | ⭐⭐ 毛孔偏大慎用，会放大纹理 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; <strong>关键原则</strong>：橄榄皮避开银白色/冷粉色高光，会显灰显&quot;金属脸&quot;。选 <strong>香槟金、蜜桃金、浅古铜色</strong>，与肤色融合后是高级的&quot;从内透出来的光&quot;。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 2 圆脸高光四点打法</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>眉弓 → 额头中央偏上</strong></span></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">竖向窄条高光，视觉拉长上庭。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>鼻梁中段（短短一截）</strong></span></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">只点在山根到鼻尖上 1/3 处，不要通刷到鼻头——否则鼻子显宽显长。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>颧骨最高点（苹果肌靠上）</strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff3e0;border-left:4px solid #ff9800;padding:8px 16px;margin:10px 0;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;color:#bf360c;font-size:13px\">⚠️ 圆脸重点：高光打在 <strong>颧骨最高点偏上、偏后</strong> 的位置（靠近太阳穴方向），而不是苹果肌正中间。这样光线把视觉焦点往上提，脸看起来更窄更立体。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">4.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>下巴尖端（一小点）</strong></span></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">配合修容的颏下阴影，让下巴更&quot;翘&quot;更V。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 3 叠加小心机</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>在高光 <strong>之前</strong>，用一点点 <strong>液体高光混进粉底</strong>，薄薄拍在颧骨最高点，再叠粉状高光 → 光泽更有层次、更&quot;皮肤感&quot;，不像浮在表面。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>鼻梁高光用 <strong>手指轻点拍按</strong>，比刷子更服帖自然。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">三、圆脸修容高光的&quot;三条红线&quot;🚫</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>修容不过瞳孔线</strong>——颧骨修容向内延伸超过瞳孔正下方，会让脸看起来更短更宽。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>高光不铺苹果肌正面</strong>——圆脸苹果肌本身饱满，正面打亮只会让脸更&quot;膨胀&quot;。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>不用珠光腮红代替高光</strong>——橄榄皮 + 毛孔偏大，大面积珠光 = 放大毛孔 + 油光感。</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff9c4;border-left:4px solid #f9a825;padding:12px 16px;margin:14px 0;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e65100\">💡 <strong>针对你的肤质/脸型：</strong></strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>角质层偏厚 + 毛孔偏大</strong>：上修容前确保底妆有做好妆前毛孔填充（毛孔隐形乳），否则粉状修容会卡进毛孔，出现&quot;麻点阴影&quot;。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>出油适中</strong>：T区出油后高光会变得过亮、失控，建议鼻梁高光用 **哑光遮</div>",
  "research": "<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 1</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">HAO YANG, Joseph Foley</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Interactional Resources Employed by Students in EFL Student-Led Group Task Interaction</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Journal of English Language and Linguistics</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">This study aimed to investigate the strategies used by students during group tasks in the EFL classroom. The study focused on translanguaging as one of the strategies to facilitate communication and interaction among students. The data was collected by recording the classroom discussions of a focused group in an EFL class at a Chinese university over three hours. The analysis was carried out using…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文与<strong>方向二（课堂互动与中介）</strong>高度相关：研究聚焦EFL课堂中学生主导的小组任务互动，以会话分析方法考察translanguaging作为互动资源的使用策略，直接涉及translanguaging和peer interaction两个核心议题。此外，研究语境设置在中国大学外语课堂，与CSL/语言教学课堂互动研究共享理论框架（如会话分析、互动能力），其对学生如何借助translanguaging协商意义、促进交流的发现，可为探讨语言相关片段（LRE）及中介化互动能力模型（MICM）提</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.62819/jel.2024.145\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.62819/jel.2024.145</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 2</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Richard Kern</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Twenty‐first century technologies and language education: Charting a path forward</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Modern Language Journal</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">55 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The COVID-19 pandemic, necessitating remote instruction in the vast majority of educational institutions around the world, put technology squarely at the center of language learning and teaching. Virtually all teaching and learning was mediated by Zoom or similar videoconferencing platforms. Students could see one another&#x27;s faces (rather than the backs of their peers’ heads), but they could also c…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文探讨了21世纪技术（尤其是疫情期间远程教学平台）对语言教育的影响，涉及课堂互动模式的根本性变化（如Zoom分组讨论、聊天窗口作为交际副渠道），这与<strong>方向二</strong>中CSL课堂互动、同伴互动（peer interaction）及中介（mediation）研究直接相关，因为技术平台重新塑造了学习者之间的互动方式与语言相关片段的生成情境。此外，技术驱动的教学变革也牵涉<strong>方向三</strong>中教师在制度性技术要求下的情感劳动与</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1111/modl.12924\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1111/modl.12924</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 3</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Kevin W. H. Tai</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Inclusive Pedagogical Practices in English-Medium Instruction Science and Mathematics Classrooms for Linguistically and Culturally Diverse Students</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Research in Science Education</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2021</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">120 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Abstract In English-medium instruction (EMI), English-as-a-second-language students will learn all/some subjects through English. Although there are a considerable number of studies which explore classroom interaction in Hong Kong (HK) secondary EMI schools, few studies have investigated EMI lessons which involve South Asian ethnic minorised students. These students share different linguistic and …</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文聚焦EMI课堂中translanguaging作为包容性教学策略的多模态会话分析，与<strong>方向二</strong>高度相关，尤其在translanguaging实践和课堂互动分析层面形成直接呼应，为理解语言多样性背景下的中介机制提供了参照。同时，研究关注语言少数族裔学生在EMI体制下的经历，涉及语言权力与教育公平议题，与<strong>方向一</strong>中语言权力和认知不公正（epistemic injustice）的关切存在潜在对话空间。此外，教师在多语多文化课堂中的教学调适也可延伸至**</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6</a></td></tr></table>\n</div>"
